GoldenEye::

She finally reached the base where KitKat was residing. She flew over 
head and checked the area. She saw in the distance that a bot was 
coming towards the base at high speed. (Destructor) She flew down to 
the entrance and transformed into bot mode. She stood there and 
waited. Perhaps this bot was one of KitKat's.  She waited.
